Note on shipped brand assets:

The following files are not covered by this MIT license. They are property of
Lully 1661 Boulangerie (Lisbon) and are shipped here with their permission as
the working reference brand for this label-generator project:

  - templates/labels/icons/figurine.svg
  - docs/design-reference/icons/figurine.svg
  - docs/design-reference/single-label.html
  - docs/design-reference/single-label.pdf
  - docs/design-reference/single-label-vector.svg
  - docs/design-reference/comparison-original-vs-reproduction.png
  - reference-pdf/Plano etiquetas (easy).pdf
  - data/labels-sample.csv (product names and prices)

If you fork this project for your own bakery, replace these files with your
own brand assets. The pipeline code (everything else) is freely reusable
under the MIT terms above.
